snippet.title: HELLDIVERS  Announce Trailer | PS4, PS3, PS Vita
snippet.description:
HELLDIVERS™ is a cross-play top-down squad shooter coming as a cross-play, cross-chat, cross-save title across the PS4™, PS3™ & PS Vita systems in 2014.

Dive into intergalactic warfare as part of the elite unit called the HELLDIVERS,  and utilize overpowered weapons and stratagems to defeat the enemies of mankind.

May contain content inappropriate for children, visit www.esrb.org for rating information.
